Setting Up the Redux:

https://medium.com/better-programming/creating-a-simple-app-with-react-js-f6aa88998952

In command prompt goto the path where you want to save your application. then run below

npm init react-app my-app-name

This will intialize the react js application and create the application with the your application name (my-app-name)

cd my-app-name

// Setting up the Redux

// core redux library

npm install --save redux
npm install --save react-redux

npm install --save-dev babel-loader babel-core babel-preset-env babel-preset-react webpack webpack-dev-server html-webpack-plugin


